{"tid":1187282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普BB英國遇刺","createTime":"2019-06-05T14:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T14:25:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a529a8fc7c2bf8fe093b8020b2e030bdcf01c6","tid":1187282,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/ftp/News/20190605/_XTA08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20190605%2F_XTA08.jpg&h=53bdae97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倫敦國會廣場外周二有反美國總統特朗普的示威者組成抗議活動，升起一個大型「特朗普寶寶」氣球，下方標語要求特朗普勿染指英國的國民保健服務。（法新社） <br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】為抗議特朗普訪問英國而升起的「特朗普寶寶」氣球，4日被一名支持特朗普民眾刺破。<br />\n<br />\n照顧氣球民眾表示，一名女子在下議院外接近示威民眾，並從其中一個迷你「特朗普寶寶」氣球背後用尖銳物品刺下。警方隨後將這名女子帶開，倫敦市警察表示，該女子因持有尖銳物品而被逮補。<br />\n<br />\n在國會廣場另一端，一名特朗普支持者意外被打到頭。影片顯示一群示威民眾對著該名男子高喊「納粹敗類」，接著就看到他被一飲料罐砸中頭部。<br />\n<br />\n倫敦市長簡世德(Sadiq Khan)領銜的大倫敦政府，允許示威民眾在特朗普訪問英國時，升起「特朗普寶寶」氣球。<br />\n<br />\n4日當地早上9點，示威民眾在議會廣場升起20呎高的「特朗普寶寶」氣球，接著也充起較小的「特朗普寶寶」氣球。特朗普當日在拜訪英國首相文翠珊時，必須繞過「特朗普寶寶」才能抵達白廳。<br />\n<br />\n「特朗普寶寶」氣球發起人之一維克史黛芙(Anna?Vickerstaff)說，氣球見證英國偉大政治歷史，向特朗普及他的仇恨政策傳達一個很明確的訊息：我們不歡迎他。<br />\n<br />\n許多示威民眾也和坐在金馬桶上推特中的機器人特朗普合照。該機器人重複說著特朗普名言「沒有勾結俄國」、「都是假新聞」。機器人訂製人利瑟姆(Don?Lessem)表示，該機器人約16呎高，和特朗普的自負一樣高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20190605/ttaa2_r.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTor%2Fhtm%2FNews%2F20190605%2Fttaa2_r.htm&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=064c32ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20190605/ttaa2_r.htm</a>"},{"pid":"c790ce0a3ffd4a2cf6f01920d64a4574df1a19b8","tid":1187282,"uid":52763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oo3vIhl6xHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Foo3vIhl6xHY&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=aa2033ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oo3vIhl6xHY</a><br />\nWe love trump!We love trump!"},{"pid":"23afe7ea3d244a0d8a6f43b157739ea3f2304d7d","tid":1187282,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:14:40.000Z","msg":"特朗普BB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4677d051ab1dd0968d5eb8b8ed06bdc6c7f067b","tid":1187282,"uid":134215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T14:25:49.000Z","msg":"氣球見證<span style=\"color: red;\">英國偉大政治歷史</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61821653_10161807638565483_2823972363266162688_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=1e2a7c6b37107682d5453cf59af55eca&amp;oe=5D8C7165\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61821653_10161807638565483_2823972363266162688_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D1e2a7c6b37107682d5453cf59af55eca%26oe%3D5D8C7165&h=5cd7488c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}